# Binary document/asset types — never line-ending-normalize.
# (Added 2026-06-12: git auto-detected the reportlab-generated
# THETIS_DIRECT_PORT_PLAN.pdf as TEXT because its ASCII85 streams
# contain no NUL bytes; a checkout under core.autocrlf=true would
# have rewritten LF -> CRLF inside it and corrupted the file.)
*.pdf  binary
*.docx binary
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.ico  binary
*.dll  binary
*.bundle binary
